================================
SITE ARCHITECTURE RULES
================================
- App Router with folder-based routing
- Each route lives in its own folder
- Each page MUST contain:
  - page.tsx
  - metadata definition (inline or via generateMetadata)
- Shared layout components:
  - Header (navigation, logo, CTA)
  - Footer (links, legal, trust)
- Reusable section components:
  - Hero
  - FeatureGrid
  - Benefits
  - CTA
  - FAQ
  - PricingCards
- Avoid deep component nesting unless reusable

